Package: MmCMS
Type: Package
Title: CMS-based Molecular Subtyping for Mouse Tissue
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(person("Raheleh", "Amirkhah", 
                    email = "r.amirkhah@qub.ac.uk",
                    role = c("aut", "cre")),
            person("Philip D.", "Dunne",
                    email = "p.dunne@qub.ac.uk",
                    role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: Raheleh Amirkhah <r.amirkhah@qub.ac.uk>
Description: This package performs CMS (Consensus Molecular Subtypes) classification on mouse tissues using pre-defined subtype templates.It supports ssGSEA score calculations with GSVA, compatible with both older GSVA versions (>= 1.26.0) and the latest updates (>= 1.48.0).
Depends: R (>= 3.5)
Imports: BiocParallel,
         GSVA (>= 1.26.0),
         graphics, 
         stats, 
         utils
Suggests: 
    commonmark,
    parallel,
    snow,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    xml2
LazyData: TRUE
Encoding: UTF-8
ByteCompile: TRUE
